A vintage 1950s advertisement style illustration of a glamorous peacock with magnificent iridescent tail feathers fully displayed, standing proudly in front of a crumbling, rusted old machine with exposed gears and worn components. The peacock's exterior is immaculately beautiful with rich blues, greens, and golds, while the machinery behind it shows signs of neglect and deterioration. The scene is set in a retro-styled showroom with warm sepia tones, aged paper texture, and subtle halftone dot patterns typical of mid-century print advertisements. Dramatic spotlight illumination highlights the contrast between the stunning surface presentation and the questionable inner workings. No text or words anywhere in the image.
